description: A pair of glass-eyed mannequins stare across the room into a gilt-framed mirror hung on a deep blue silk-covered wall.  At the far end of the wagon, ceiling mounted racks create a colorful exhibit of garments, while fine jewelry is showcased beneath the glass of a gold-framed display case.
title: [The Tailored Imperial, Showroom]
location: between Wehnimer's Landing and Zul Logoth
